        ----
        
        Web API Interface for Scratch!
        
        Rewrite of scratchapi2 + scratchapi, with additional features and easier usage and readability!
        
        To use this plugin, you must first install requests, if pip does not automatically install it when you install BetterScratchAPI.
        Mac/Linux:
        ```python
        python3 -m pip install requests
        ```
        Windows:
        ```
        pip install requests
        ```
        
